org.projectodd.sockjs

Class SockJsServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.projectodd.sockjs.SockJsServer

  • public class SockJsServer
extends Object
    The main entry point for handling SockJS connections. Typically a SockJsServer is created, its options set, an onConnection(org.projectodd.sockjs.SockJsServer.OnConnectionHandler) handler added, and the server is then passed to a SockJsServlet to handle the routing of requests.
